title: Bridlington Bay Block 1
description: This processed bathymetric data set has been derived from an Echosounder - single beam survey. The source data was collected, validated and processed for the purpose of Safety Of Life At Sea (SOLAS). The data set must not be used for navigation or to create products that could be used for navigation.
